{"tid":1119720,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"搞野真係好重要","createTime":"2019-04-22T06:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T18:53:29.000Z","uid":31167,"like":58,"dislike":736,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d37f37252d8e4134495f1905431552076f7e3a","tid":1119720,"uid":31167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:45:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的 最初同男友搞野果時真係會整濕成張床<br />\n直至拍拖第4個年頭 依家同男友搞野已經愈來愈唔識濕 仲好乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n硬係覺得佢搞我只為咗自己 我覺得自己好似肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似所有男人都係為屌而屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾終於分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過咗半年 有個tb不停追我 但我地無一齊 <br />\n有次飲完酒 tb搞我 我濕到好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次同女人搞野 我好緊張 不安&hellip;<br />\n但唔明點解可以覺得舒服過以往同男人搞野咁 到底我係直定les<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我地關係好似sp咁&hellip;到底我應該揀返個男人拍拖 定 試下同tb一齊？<br />\n<br />\n利申 27歲 以往拍拖對像都係男性"},{"pid":"f901a6d5d799e571487c65fdef88cd61e10bb4c6","tid":1119720,"uid":61005,"like":338,"dislike":6,"score":332,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"e2a3c227f964de8389cca4e40ad98e3b2dc355e4","tid":1119720,"uid":31167,"like":4,"dislike":53,"score":-49,"quote":{"pid":"f901a6d5d799e571487c65fdef88cd61e10bb4c6","tid":1119720,"uid":61005,"like":338,"dislike":6,"score":332,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"0/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"我講真㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b93f90e4fbc86a758e3f8a02d339e1982aacb8e","tid":1119720,"uid":36402,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:50:33.000Z","msg":"是但啦 有野就搞咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47befc9920e6a68fab7cb090c9f678294fc54b2f","tid":1119720,"uid":201944,